# CODEOWNERS — Loop
#
# Each path is automatically reviewed by the owners listed. Lines further
# down win; later patterns override earlier ones (GitHub semantics).
#
# Owner mappings derive from architecture/ARCHITECTURE.md §15 (service
# ownership matrix) + engineering/HANDBOOK.md §3.4. Roles are placeholder
# GitHub team handles inside the @loop-ai org. They MUST be created (with
# at least one human member each) before branch protection is turned on,
# otherwise required reviews cannot be satisfied.
#
# See docs/branch-protection.md for the GitHub admin checklist.

